size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Altre filiali</span></p><p>Luisenstrasse 19, 8005 Zurigo<br />(per gli orari, ved. <a href="http://www.michellescupcakes.ch/" target="_blank">sito Internet</a>)</p>','Michelle’s Cupcakes ','Michelle’s Cupcakes','Michelle’s Cupcakes','Michelle’s Cupcakes','Süsses, Salziges, Flüssiges und Haugemachtes gibt’s in diesem wunderbaren kleinen Laden.','Salty, savory, liquid, and homemade can all be found in this wonderful little store.','Cette superbe boutique propose du sucré, du salé, du liquide et du fait maison.','Delizie dolci, salate, liquide e artigianali si trovano in questo incantevole negozietto.',NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_restaurant_cupcake_01.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_cafe_michellescupcakes_05.jpg','2019-09-25 10:11:02 +0200','Regionale, lokale Delikatessen',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Die Filiale am Talacker 34','The branch at Talacker 34','L''autre succursale, au Talacker 34
